<topic class="popup" template="Popup" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Tip #43</title>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Heading3"><text styleclass="Heading3" translate="true">Tip of the Day</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table rowcount="1" colcount="2" style="cell-padding:0px; cell-spacing:0px; border-width:0px; cell-border-width:0px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:58px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="TipOfTheDayBulb.jpg" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:328px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">There are a number of handy accelerator key sequences linked to common code refactorings: </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Ctrl+T - </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">Extract to Temporary</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, Ctrl+Shift+T -</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true"> Inline Temporary</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, F2 - </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">Rename Selection</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, Ctrl+[ - </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">Move Temporary to Inner Scope</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, Ctrl+M - </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">Extract to Method</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, Ctrl+Shift+M - </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true"> Inline Message</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">You can find out all of the accelerators available in any tool by choosing </text><text styleclass="Menu Command" translate="true">Help/Key Bindings</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. Please note that the refactorings are only available in Dolphin Professional.</text><snippet src="Tip_Of_The_Day_Footer"/></para>
  </body>
</topic>
